### Vercel (`user-vercel` and `plugin-vercel-vercel`)

Two entries share the Vercel name; disambiguate by **server** string above. Prefer MCP for Vercel work when tools work; use **Vercel CLI** (`npx vercel deploy --prod`, etc.) if a tool is a stub (e.g. `deploy_to_vercel` may only return text) or teams/projects API is empty.

