**Tools (20):** `apply_migration`, `create_branch`, `delete_branch`, `merge_branch`, `rebase_branch`, `reset_branch`, `list_branches`, `deploy_edge_function`, `get_edge_function`, `list_edge_functions`, `execute_sql` (migrations for DDL), `list_migrations`, `list_tables`, `list_extensions`, `generate_typescript_types`, `get_advisors`, `get_logs`, `get_project_url`, `get_publishable_keys`, `search_docs`

