## Auth (MCP)

If a server exposes `mcp_auth`, use it when needed. **One** `mcp_auth` at a time (not parallel).

## Memory

The agent has **no** persistent memory across sessions; **this rule + git** are the project‚Äôs ‚Äúremembered‚Äù conventions.

